    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether combination of antidepressant drugs plus
      interpersonal psychotherapy is superior to antidepressant drugs alone in treatment resistant
      depression.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
